00:56:38.170 --> 00:56:42.510
but in the reality of living their lives,
if they'd been following the religious leadership

00:56:42.510 --> 00:56:45.340
they had, they would not have been involved.

00:56:45.340 --> 00:56:50.000
The religious leadership, the clergy, weren't
always setting the examples.

00:56:50.000 --> 00:56:51.800
