00:57:19.869 --> 00:57:21.830
He had the thorn in this case.

00:57:21.830 --> 00:57:23.900
So it's a mixed bag, who's going to help,
who's not.

00:57:23.900 --> 00:57:25.630
Is their religion driving them?

00:57:25.630 --> 00:57:29.020
I think if you look more just as you draw
conclusions, there was a moral character.

00:57:29.020 --> 00:57:32.200
Whether it came from their Catholicism or
not, it was there.

00:57:32.200 --> 00:57:36.470
If the Catholicism was not supporting it,
they would have the moral character to go,

00:57:36.470 --> 00:57:38.150
"We're going to still do the right thing."

00:57:38.150 --> 00:57:39.800
The ethics comes through.

